Penguin tried to waddle out of the way, but some of the blasts ripped
into his armor as he moved, he tried to roll, but his ungainly Penguin
form caused him to slip. He quickly transformed into train mode, and
began to gain some momentum again, this time rocketing forward a bit, he
came to a stop, and began to charge Manthys.
